page.title: 19Famous People
page.content: {Eric Morecambe Eric Bartholomew was born in Morecambe in the 1920's,he was about 60 when he died in 1984. Eric changed his name to Morecambe when he became a comedian. He had a partner called Ernie Wise. At the peak of their career they were invited to America but they refused. {Victoria Wood Victoria was born in Morecambe and began her career as a singer and comedienne in clubs. Then she appeared on television with Julie Walters in a progamme called Walters and Wood. Now she has her own programmes. {Helen Worth Helen was born in Morecambe in the 1950's. She is an actress in Coronation Street where she plays Gail Tilsey. Her mother lives in Morecambe and owns a shop in the West End.
